==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Anatiferous
<hw>An`a*tif"er*ous</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>anas</ets>, <ets>anatis</ets>, a duck + <ets>-ferous</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Producing ducks; -- applied to
<xex>Anatif⟦ae⟧</xex>, under the absurd notion of their turning into
ducks or geese. See <er>Barnacle</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Anatine</ent>⟦br⟧
